ply_by": "unco020511", "last_touched": 1705042880, "title": "人在境外因联通手机号涉案被民警要求去异地配合调查", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1007987", "created": 1705020973, "deleted": 0, "content": "前情 https://v2ex.com/t/965316\r\n去年 11 月初联系天津市滨海新区公安局后有一个民警加我 v 跟我介绍情况 然而通话详单调两个多月了没结果 就跟我耗着 也没提解决方案 遂投诉天津市长信箱\r\nhttps://i.imgur.com/Bto8QYF.png\r\nhttps://i.imgur.com/2VRL7W3.png\r\nhttps://i.imgur.com/Gs1slMg.png\r\nhttps://i.imgur.com/nCLoRDd.png\r\n\r\n投诉后有警员跟我接洽 声称手机号涉嫌电信诈骗是管控中 不是停机/冻结了 会有主管加我给我看通话详单\r\nhttps://i.imgur.com/wkHjatK.png\r\nhttps://i.imgur.com/tFnEEy4.png\r\n\r\n主管（另一名办案民警？）加我微信 直接让我去天津配合调查 我要看通话详单 说我去了会给我展示证据\r\nhttps://i.imgur.com/iUZowmC.png\r\nhttps://i.imgur.com/h5Xj3ld.png\r\n\r\n我号码被封没人通知我 我要维权得自己跑一趟 还有这种事\r\n有没有懂的 还能怎么操作\r\n12389 公安部举报中心投诉后无响应 12345 市长热线不管刑事案件\r\n实在不行只能换个号了 不知道开新号会不会受影响", "content_rendered": "前情 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://v2ex.com/t/965316\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://v2ex.com/t/965316</a><br />去年 11 月初联系天津市滨海新区公安局后有一个民警加我 v 跟我介绍情况 然而通话详单调两个多月了没结果 就跟我耗着 也没提解决方案 遂投诉天津市长信箱<br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Bto8QYF.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Bto8QYF.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/2VRL7W3.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2VRL7W3.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Gs1slMg.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Gs1slMg.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/nCLoRDd.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nCLoRDd.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><br />投诉后有警员跟我接洽 声称手机号涉嫌电信诈骗是管控中 不是停机/冻结了 会有主管加我给我看通话详单<br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wkHjatK.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wkHjatK.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/tFnEEy4.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tFnEEy4.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><br />主管（另一名办案民警？）加我微信 直接让我去天津配合调查 我要看通话详单 说我去了会给我展示证据<br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/iUZowmC.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iUZowmC.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/h5Xj3ld.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/h5Xj3ld.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><br />我号码被封没人通知我 我要维权得自己跑一趟 还有这种事<br />有没有懂的 还能怎么操作<br />12389 公安部举报中心投诉后无响应 12345 市长热线不管刑事案件<br />实在不行只能换个号了 不知道开新号会不会受影响", "last_modified": 1705020973, "replies": 153, "id": 1007987}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_large.png?m=1644885960", "name": "car", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_normal.png?m=1644885960", "title": "汽车", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/car", "topics": 1883, "footer": "", "header": "关于买车、开车及汽车文化的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Car", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960", "stars": 1723, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 176, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 531754, "username": "Satella", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Satella", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4b64/e62a/531754_mini.png?m=1705040942", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4b64/e62a/531754_normal.png?m=1705040942", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4b64/e62a/531754_large.png?m=1705040942", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4b64/e62a