errer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dlRaw5s.jpg\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1705025286, "replies": 73, "id": 1008018}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1700771269", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1700771269", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 60852, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1700771269", "stars": 8805, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 406032, "username": "lbunderway", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/lbunderway", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7950/2df8/406032_mini.png?m=1676946658", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7950/2df8/406032_normal.png?m=1676946658", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7950/2df8/406032_large.png?m=1676946658", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7950/2df8/406032_xlarge.png?m=1676946658", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7950/2df8/406032_xlarge.png?m=1676946658", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7950/2df8/406032_xlarge.png?m=1676946658", "created": 1556172011, "last_modified": 1676946658}, "last_reply_by": "SenLief", "last_touched": 1705042338, "title": "后端接口规范问题，只提供一个接口如何？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1007821", "created": 1704957435, "deleted": 0, "content": "一个后端服务只向外提供一个借口，全用 post ，通过定义不同的业务 code 进行处理，我之前有个小系统就这样搞过，并且我还觉得前端反而会不会简单些，只用一个接口，而有的项目用 rest 风格，有的反而有点不伦不类，大佬些觉得如何呢", "content_rendered": "<p>一个后端服务只向外提供一个借口，全用 post ，通过定义不同的业务 code 进行处理，我之前有个小系统就这样搞过，并且我还觉得前端反而会不会简单些，只用一个接口，而有的项目用 rest 风格，有的反而有点不伦不类，大佬些觉得如何呢</p>\n", "last_modified": 1704957435, "replies": 66, "id": 1007821}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_large.png?m=1630576706", "name": "invest", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_normal.png?m=1630576706", "title": "投资", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/invest", "topics": 1361, "footer": "", "header": "Can you make money with money?", "title_alternative": "Invest", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_mini.png?m=1630576706", "stars": 2460, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 171, "parent_node_name": "money"}, "member": {"id": 467166, "username": "BlueHat514", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/BlueHat514", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9dff64d6f53d131a1228b332192333dd?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9dff64d6f53d131a1228b332192333dd?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9dff64d6f53d131a1228b332192333dd?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1580360764, "last_modified": 1700889096}, "last_reply_by": "cbythe434", "last_touched": 1705041589, "title": "在中国普通个人如何对冲房地产的不确定风险？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1008009", "created": 1705023879, "deleted": 0, "content": "我们都知道，在金融期货中，生产者可以通过期货来消除对未来价格变动的不确定风险。\r\n\r\n例如假设大豆的生产者觉得现在的大豆价格非常合适，但是大豆要一年后才能成熟，担心一年后的价格大幅缩水，导致自己赚不到钱。\r\n\r\n他的对策是立刻在期货市场中购买等买等额的大豆期货空单。如果一年后大豆价格上涨，现货赚钱，期货亏钱；如果一年后大豆价格下降，现货亏钱，期货赚钱。从而对冲了未来的不确定风险，提前锁定了利润。\r\n\r\n那么在房地产中，普通个人是否有类似的渠道来对冲掉这种不确定性风险呢？", "content_rendered": "我们都知道，在金融期货中，生产者可以通过期货来消除对未来价格变动的不确定风险。<br /><br />例如假设大豆的生产者觉得现在的大豆价格非常合适，但是大豆要一年后才能成熟，担心一年后的价格大幅缩水，导致自己赚不到钱。<br /><br />他的对策是立刻在期货市场中购买等买等额的大豆期货空单。如果一年后大豆价格上涨，现货赚钱，期货亏钱；如果一年后大豆价格下降，现货亏钱，期货赚钱。从而对冲了未来的不确定风险，提前锁定了利润。<br /><br />那么在房地产中，普通个人是否有类似的渠道来对冲掉这种不确定性风险呢？", "last_modified": 1705034938, "replies": 61, "id": 1008009}]